ANNOUNCEMENT: 

The UC Berkeley Memes for Edgy Teens administrative and moderating team are happy to announce our official partnership with Sizzler™ (Now you’re talking). Sizzler™ (Now you’re talking) brings the choices that you’ve been looking for and by giving you the right to choose, we’re offering you much more! By holding to traditions yet changing with the times, choices and selections, choices of directions, choices that can add a little freedom of your life. Sizzler™ (Now you’re talking) is the choice of America! Sizzler™ (Now you’re talking) gives you choices everyday. That’s the Sizzler™ (Now you’re talking) way! Get a little freedom in your life!

In other news: the UC Berkeley Memes for Edgy Teens administrative and moderating team will be taking applications for moderators. If you are interested please send someone a cover letter and a résumé. 

Have a blessed day!
